Packages 
Package Description
pacman.game
Main game package that contains all the packages required for the game to function.
pacman.game.actors
Deprecated Package.
pacman.game.ai
Package containing Pacman and Ghosts creation and AI.
pacman.game.ai.agents
Package containing the functions and classes for the creation of the AI of the entities.
pacman.game.ai.astar
Package containing the classes related to pathfinding and tracking.
pacman.game.ashley.components
Package containing the entity creating functions and classes.
pacman.game.ashley.systems
Package containing the control of entity physics and behaviours.
pacman.game.controller
Package containing inputController class responsible for reading inputs from the device being used.
pacman.game.helpers
Package containing all the body factories, main game settings, materials and other helping functions.
pacman.game.model
Package containing the main game creation functions.
pacman.game.views
Package containing the different screen available in the game, such as settings and main menu.
